{"kanda":6,"sarga":66,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"स लङ्घयित्वाप्राकारंगिरिकूटोपमोमहान् ।निर्ययौनगरात्तूर्णंकुम्भकर्णोमहाबलः","trans":"Mighty Kumbhakarna, a gigantic one, resembling a mountain peak, having swiftly crossed over the boundary of the city roared.","words":[{"d":"गिरिकूटोपमः","m":"who resembled peak of mountain"},{"d":"महान्","m":"gigantic"},{"d":"महाबलः","m":"mighty"},{"d":"सःकुम्भकर्ण:","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"प्राकारं","m":"boundary"},{"d":"लङ्घयित्वा","m":"having crossed"},{"d":"तूर्णम्","m":"swiftly"},{"d":"नगरात्","m":"from the city"},{"d":"निर्ययौ","m":"roared."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"ननाद च महानादंसमुद्रमभिनादयन् ।विजयन्निवनिर्घातन्विधमन्निवपर्वतान्","trans":"Kumbhakarna roared making loud noises as if proclaiming victory, like the breaking of mountains and reverberating of ocean.","words":[{"d":"निर्घातान्","m":"bringing out loud noise,विजयत्रि as if proclaiming victory"},{"d":"पर्वतान्","m":"mountains"},{"d":"विधमन् इव","m":"like breaking"},{"d":"महानादम्","m":"great sound"},{"d":"समुद्रम्","m":"ocean"},{"d":"अभिनादयन्","m":"reverberate"},{"d":"नादयन","m":"roared."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"तमवध्यंमघवतायमेनवरुणेनवा ।प्रेक्ष्यभीमाक्षमायान्तंवानराविप्रदुद्रुवुः","trans":"Observing that rakshasa with frightening eyes, who could not be killed by Indra or Yama or even by Varuna coming towards them the vanaras ran in fear.","words":[{"d":"मघवता","m":"by Indra"},{"d":"वरुणेनवा","m":"or even Varuna"},{"d":"अवध्यम्","m":"not be killed"},{"d":"भीमाक्षम्","m":"with frightening eyes"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him"},{"d":"प्रेक्ष्य","m":"observing"},{"d":"वानराः","m":"the Vanaras"},{"d":"विप्रदुद्रुवुः","m":"ran in fear."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"तांस्तुविप्रद्रुतान् दृष्टवाराजपुत्रोऽङ्गदोऽब्रवीत् ।नलंनीलंगवाक्षं च कुमुदं च महाबलम्","trans":"Seeing the Vanaras running in fear, Angada spoke to Nala, Nila, Gavaksha, Mahabala and Kumuda.","words":[{"d":"विप्रद्रुतान्","m":"running in fear"},{"d":"तान्","m":"them"},{"d":"नलम्","m":"Nala"},{"d":"नीलम्","m":"Nila"},{"d":"गवाक्षं च","m":"and Gavaksha"},{"d":"महाबलम्","m":"Mahabala"},{"d":"कुमुदम्","m":"Kumuda"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"राजपुत्रः","m":"prince"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"आत्मानमत्रविस्मृत्यवीर्याण्यभिजनानि च ।क्वगच्छतभयत्रस्ताःप्राकृताहरयोयथा","trans":"\"Forgetting yourself, that you are warriors, not knowing by nature, being Vanaras where are you going?\"","words":[{"d":"आत्मानम्","m":"yourself"},{"d":"अत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"वीर्याणि","m":"warriors"},{"d":"अभिजनानि च","m":"not knowing"},{"d":"विस्मृत्य","m":"forgetting"},{"d":"प्राकृताः","m":"by nature"},{"d":"हरयःयथा","m":"like the Vanaras"},{"d":"भयत्रस्ताः","m":"fearing"},{"d":"क्व","m":"where"},{"d":"गच्छत","m":"are you going."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"साधुसौम्या निवर्तध्वंकिप्राणान्परिरक्षथ ।नालंयुद्धायवैरक्षोमहतीयंबिभीषका","trans":"\"O good Vanaras! You are modest. Return. Why are you protecting your life? This Rakshasa is not capable of facing war. He can create only fear.\"","words":[{"d":"सौम्याः","m":"good"},{"d":"साधु","m":"modest"},{"d":"निवर्तध्वम्","m":"return"},{"d":"प्राणान्","m":"life"},{"d":"किम्","m":"why"},{"d":"परिरक्षथ","m":"protecting"},{"d":"रक्षः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"युद्धाय","m":"in war"},{"d":"नालम्","m":"not capable facing"},{"d":"इयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"महती","m":"great"},{"d":"बिभीषिका","m":"who can create fear."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"महतीमुथतितामेनांराक्षसानांबिभीषिकाम् ।विक्रमाद्विधमिष्यामोनिवर्तध्वंप्लवङ्गमाः","trans":"\"O Vanaras! We will dispel this huge rakshasa, a nightmare with our power. Come back.\"","words":[{"d":"प्लवङ्गमाः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"राक्षसानाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"उथतिताम्","m":"dispel"},{"d":"महतीम्","m":"huge"},{"d":"एनांबिभीषिकाम्","m":"this nightmare"},{"d":"विक्रमात्","m":"with our power"},{"d":"विधमिष्यामः","m":"kill them"},{"d":"निवर्तध्वम्","m":"come back."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"कृच्छ्रेणतुसमाश्वस्यसङ्गम्य च ततस्ततः ।वृक्षाद्रिहस्ताहरयस्सम्प्रतस्थूरणाजिरम्","trans":"Overcoming fear, the Vanaras getting together from here and there holding trees by