ामः","m":"will fight."}]},{"v":19,"dev":"भग्नानांवो न पश्यामिपरिगम्यमहीमिमाम् स्थानंसर्वेनिवर्तध्वंकिंप्राणान् परिरक्षथ ।","trans":"\"I do not see any refuge for you even if you go round the globe. All of you return back. Why do you preserve life?\"","words":[{"d":"इमाम्","m":"this"},{"d":"महीम्","m":"globe"},{"d":"परिक्रम्य","m":"go round"},{"d":"भग्नानाम्","m":"routed"},{"d":"वः","m":"or"},{"d":"स्थानम्","m":"place"},{"d":"न पश्यामि","m":"not see"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"निवर्तध्वम्","m":"return"},{"d":"प्राणान्","m":"life"},{"d":"किम्","m":"why"},{"d":"परिरक्षथ","m":"refuge."}]},{"v":20,"dev":"निरायुधानांद्रवतामसङ्गगतिपौरुषाः दाराह्युपहसिष्यन्ति स वैघातस्तुजीवताम् ।","trans":"\"Monkeys! Your valour can't be challenged. If you run away for life abandoning weapons even your wives will ridicule you. That is more than death.\"","words":[{"d":"असङ्गगतिपौरुषाः","m":"whose valour can't be challenged"},{"d":"निरायुधानाम्","m":"abandoning weapons"},{"d":"द्रवताम्","m":"run away"},{"d":"दाराः","m":"wives"},{"d":"उपहसिष्यन्ति","m":"will ridicule"},{"d":"जीवताम्","m":"life"},{"d":"सः","m":"for those"},{"d":"घातःवै","m":"indeed more than death."}]},{"v":21,"dev":"कुलेषुजातास्सर्वेस्मविस्तीर्णेषुमहत्सु च क्वगच्छतभयत्रस्ताःहरयःप्राकृतायथा ।अनार्याःखलुयद्भीतास्त्यक्त्वावीर्यंप्रधावत","trans":"\"You are born in noble families, and are widely spread. As such why are you running away like ordinary monkeys as if terrified giving up your valour. It is not worthy of you.\"","words":[{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"विस्तीर्णेषु","m":"widely spread"},{"d":"महत्सु च","m":"noble also"},{"d":"कुलेषु","m":"clan"},{"d":"जाताःस्म","m":"born into"},{"d":"प्राकृताः","m":"ordinary"},{"d":"हरयःयथा","m":"monkeys like"},{"d":"भयत्रस्ताः","m":"in fear"},{"d":"क्व","m":"why"},{"d":"गच्छत","m":"go"},{"d":"वीर्यम्","m":"valour"},{"d":"त्यक्त्वा","m":"giving up"},{"d":"भीताः","m":"terrified"},{"d":"यत्","m":"as if"},{"d":"प्रधावत","m":"running away"},{"d":"अनार्याःखलु","m":"not worthy of."}]},{"v":