ear"},{"d":"त्यज्यताम्","m":"giving up."}]},{"v":25,"dev":"शयामहेऽनिहताःपृथिव्यामल्पजीविताः ।दुष्प्रापंब्रह्मलोकंवाप्राप्नुयामोयुधिसूदिता","trans":"\"If we are killed in war, fallen dead on the ground and our life span is reduced, we will attain the realm of Brahma which is difficult to attain.\"","words":[{"d":"अल्पजीविताः","m":"life span is reduced"},{"d":"निहताः","m":"having been killed"},{"d":"पृथिव्याम्","m":"in the world"},{"d":"युधिसूदिता","m":"killed in war"},{"d":"दुष्प्रापम्","m":"difficult to attain"},{"d":"ब्रह्मलोकम्","m":"world of Brahma"},{"d":"प्राप्नुयामः च","m":"will attain."}]},{"v":26,"dev":"सम्प्राप्नुयामःकीर्तिंवानिहत्वाशत्रुमाहवे ।जीवितंवीरलोकस्यमोक्ष्यामोवसुवानराः","trans":"\"By killing the enemy, we will attain fame. Or else we will attain the world of Brahma, liberated.\"","words":[{"d":"वानराः","m":"Vanara"},{"d":"आहवे","m":"we will"},{"d":"शत्रुम्","m":"the enemy"},{"d":"निहत्वा","m":"killing"},{"d":"कीर्तिम्","m":"fame"},{"d":"सम्प्राप्नुयामः","m":"will attain"},{"d":"वा","m":"or else"},{"d":"जीवितः","m":"life"},{"d":"वीरलोकस्य","m":"in the world of Brahma"},{"d":"वसु","m":"will be"},{"d":"मोक्ष्यामः","m":"liberated."}]},{"v":27,"dev":"न कुम्भकर्णःकाकुत्स्थंदृष्टवाजीवन् गमिष्यति ।दीप्यमानमिवासाद्यपतङ्गोज्वलनंयथा","trans":"\"Just as flies reaching the blazing fire can't escape, so also Kumbhakarna can't escape with life after facing Kakuthsa.\"","words":[{"d":"पतङ्गः","m":"fly"},{"d":"दीप्यमानम्","m":"reaching flame"},{"d":"ज्वलनम्","m":"blazing"},{"d":"आसाद्यइवयथा","m":"not possible to escape"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णः","m":"for Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"काकुत्स्थम्","m":"Kakuthsa"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"जीवन्","m":"life"},{"d":"न गच्छति","m":"not escape."}]},{"v":28,"dev":"लायनेनचोद्धिष्टाःप्राणान् रक्षामहेवयम् ।एकेनबहवोभग्नायशोनाशंगमिष्यति","trans":"\"Even though we are distinguished, if we preserve our life by running away for life, destroyed by one, our glory will come to an end.\"","words":[{"d":"एकेन","m":"by one"},{"d":"भग्नाः","m":"destroyed"},{"d":"बहवः","m":"though many"},{"d":"उददिष्टाः","m":"distinguished"},{"d":"वयम्","m":"we"},{"d":"पलायनने","m":"by running away"},{"d":"प्राणान्","m":"life"},{"d":"रक्षामहे","m":"protect"},{"d":"यशः","m":"glory"},{"d":"नाशम्","m":"gone"},{"d":"गमिष्यति","m":"come to an end."}]},{"v":29,"dev":"एवंब्रुवाणंतंशूरमङ्गदंकनकाङ्गदम् ।द्रवमाणास्ततोवाक्यमूचुःशूरुविगर्हितम्","trans":"While the heroic Angada, adorned with gold armlets, was speaking in that manner to the fleeing vanara heroes, condemned by the hero the vanaras replied as follows.","words":[{"d":"द्रवमाणाः","m":"fleeing away"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that manner"},{"d":"ब्रुवाणम्","m":"speaking"},{"d":"कनकाङ्गदम्","m":"adorned with gold armlets"},{"d":"शूरम्","m":"to the heroes"},{"d":"तम्","m":"that"},{"d":"अङ्गदम्","m":"Angada"},{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"शूरुविगर्हितम्","m":"condemned by hero"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"ऊचुः","m":"said."}]},{"v":30,"dev":"कृतंनःकदनंघोरंकुम्भकर्णेनरक्षसा ।न स्थानकालोगच्छामोदयितंजीवितंहिनः","trans":"\"Kumbhakarna, the Rakshasa has done havoc to us. This is not the moment to stay. Our life is dear to us.\"","words":[{"d":"नः","m":"us"},{"d":"रक्षसा","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"घोरम्","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"कदनम्","m":"havoc"},{"d":"कृतम्","m":"done"},{"d":"स्थानकालः","m":"moment to stay"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"नः","m":"we"},{"d":"जीवितम्","m":"our life"},{"d":"दयितंहि","m":"dear to us."}]},{"v":31,"dev":"एतावदुक्त्वावचनंसर्वेतेभेजिरेदिशः ।भीमंभीमाक्षमायान्तंदृष्टवावानरयूथपाः","trans":"All the Vanara troops having replied that way, seeing Kumbhakarna of frightful eyes coming towards them, scattered in all directions.","words":[{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all,एता to you. वानरयूथपाः Vanara troops"},{"d":"भीमाक्षम्","m":"frightful eyes"},{"d":"भीमम्","m":"fear"},{"d":"आयान्तम्","m":"coming towards"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"एतावत्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्त्वा","m":"having spoken"},{"d":"दिशः","m":"directions"},{"d":"भेजिरे","m":"scattered."}]},{"v":32,"dev"